'''白俄罗斯共和国国家银行'''（{{lang-en|'''N'''ATIONAL '''B'''ANK OF THE '''R'''EPUBLIC OF '''B'''ELARUS}}，简称'''NBRB'''）是[[白俄罗斯共和国|白俄罗斯共和国]]的[[中央银行|中央银行]]，是[[白俄罗斯卢布|白俄罗斯卢布]]的发行机构。总部位于白俄罗斯[[首都|首都]][[明斯克|明斯克]]。其根据《白俄罗斯共和国[[宪法|宪法]]》，《白俄罗斯共和国银行法》以及[[白俄罗斯总统|白俄罗斯总统]]颁布的监管法律，独立进行业务活动。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nbrb.by/engl/today/general.asp|title=General information of NATIONAL BANK OF THE REPUBLIC OF BELARUS|accessdate=2014-12-03|author=|last=|first=|authorlink=|coauthors=|date=|year=|month=|format=|work=|publisher='''''NBRB'''''|pages=|language=en|doi=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141109121114/http://www.nbrb.by/engl/today/general.asp|archivedate=2014-11-09|quote=The National Bank of the Republic of Belarus (hereinafter referred to as the "National Bank") is the central bank and a government agency of the Republic of Belarus operating exclusively in the interests of the Republic of Belarus. In performing its activities, the National Bank shall be guided by the Constitution of the Republic of Belarus , the Banking Code of the Republic of Belarus , laws of the Republic of Belarus, regulatory legal acts of the President of the Republic of Belarus, and the Statute of the National Bank of the Republic of Belarus pdf and shall be independent in its activities.|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

